mdRecord.dcterms:title: 1993 Rockefeller family holiday card
mdRecord.dcterms:creator: Rockefeller, John D., IV (John Davison), 1937-
mdRecord.dcterms:description: The 1993 Rockefeller family holiday card reads, "Wishing you a world of peace and happiness." Pictured are Jay, Sharon, Valerie, John, Justin, and Charles Rockefeller. On the back is an unofficial seal of the United States Senate.
